title: the 1
description:
Taylor Swift kicks off the folklore era strong with this song about someone who was almost the one! What all is she referencing in this song? And what is the underlying saga behind the album? We explain in our first deep dive into folklore!
What did we miss? What would you like from us? There are lots of ways to reach us!
